      "title": "Fuel license is affected by technical errors",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that the pilot project of providing fuel according to the National Fuel License is delayed due to technical glitches.",
        "This pilot project using 5 filling stations in Colombo city was scheduled to start today (21st), but it was stopped due to a technical error."
